Paper: hep-th/9902162

Date: 1999-02-23

Title: On the Beta Function in Supersymmetric Gauge Theories

Authors: G. Carlino, K. Konishi, N. Maggiore and N. Magnoli

Comments: 11 pages, LaTeX2e

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B455 (1999) 171-178

We re-examine perturbative and nonperturbative aspects of the beta functionin N=1 and N=2 supersymmetric gauge theories, make comments on the recentliterature on the subject and discuss the exactness of several known resultssuch as the NSVZ beta function.